@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ibshrb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.13
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.cos(v1 + 0.06) - wp.abs(v2 + 0.59)))
    tmp = wp.sin(v0)
    v1 = (wp.abs((v0 + 1.00 / v0 + 0.45)) / ((v2 + 0.82 / tmp + 0.38) - (v2 + 0.95 / v0 + 0.21)))
    v1 = (v1 / (0.99 - wp.exp(v0 + 0.44)))
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.23) / wp.cos(tmp + 0.74)) * 0.05)
    v0 = 0.62
    data[tid] = v0
